Martin BRAUN, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 4612. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fourth Circuit. June 11, 1940. Martin Braun, pro se. Bernard J. Flynn, U. S. Atty., of Baltimore, Md., for appellee.

Before PARKER, SOPER, and NORTHCOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The order appealed from will be affirmed on the authority of Cundiff v. Nicholson, 4 Cir., 107 F.2d 162.

Affirmed.
